{
  "chapter": 13,
  "chapter_summary": "第十三回 峰回路又转\n\n朱七七与熊猫儿潜入魔窟小楼探查，熊猫儿装醉闹事，朱七七误以为熊猫儿醉酒胡闹。实际上熊猫儿与沈浪、王怜花早已暗中联手，共同对抗快乐王的威胁。沈浪通过敏锐的观察力发现了王森记棺材铺与香烛铺互换的秘密，揭穿了王怜花的计谋。朱七七发现真相后愤怒离去，独自在城脚下痛哭，最终冷静下来后意识到还有许多疑问需要解答。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "算你有本事，但……但你也不该将他灌成如此模样。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "女人……女人……你帮着她时，她反帮着别人……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哼！",
      "tone": "冷哼",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你喝酒未醉，莫要吃醋却吃醉了。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好酒好酒，再来一壶……",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你疯了么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "疯了疯了，喝酒最好……",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不好，你……你真的醉了？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你这样试法，岂非要人的命么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好，你不叫我试，我就不试。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "嘘——莫要说话。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但愿他真的没有醉，否则……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "蠢猫，醉猫，我才真的要揍死你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好姑娘，莫要揍死我……只揍个半死就好了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "听得懂，听得懂。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你还敢不敢再吵？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不敢了，不敢了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "就……就是那里。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "咱们先去瞧瞧。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "先瞧瞧固然不错，但你却永远也猜不到小楼中那妇人有多可怕，何况，你又如此醉了……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "无妨。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "完了……完了……",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁叫你酒醉误事，谁叫你逞能灌酒，你……你……你死了也是活该，我半点也不会怜悯你……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "恐惧",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么人？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你究竟是什么东西？你……",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "站稳了，莫摔倒。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他们说你未必敢闯进来，但我却说你一定会闯进来的，我……",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "住口！你们全都给我住口！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "姑娘有话好说，何必……",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我……我……",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 362,
      "line_end": 362
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你骗我，你为什么要骗我？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这……这……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 368,
      "line_end": 368
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "此事其中委实有许多曲折，但在下……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 372,
      "line_end": 372
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但我们如此对你，却绝无恶意。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 374,
      "line_end": 374
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "此中秘密，我们本要告诉你的……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 382,
      "line_end": 382
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那你们为何不说。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 384,
      "line_end": 384
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你如此模样，却叫我等如何说话。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 386,
      "line_end": 386
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但姑娘总也该听完在下等的话，再发脾气也不迟。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 394,
      "line_end": 394
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "正是如此，你且好生坐下，且听我等向你解释。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 396,
      "line_end": 396
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我偏不坐下，你又怎样。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 398,
      "line_end": 398
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好！此事说来话长，还是请王兄从头说起。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 402,
      "line_end": 402
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "自然要说的，但……",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 412,
      "line_end": 412
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "还但什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 414,
      "line_end": 414
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好，我先问你——",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 420,
      "line_end": 420
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不知从何而来，也不知去向哪里",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 430,
      "line_end": 430
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我先问你，这是什么人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 479,
      "line_end": 479
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "家师……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 481,
      "line_end": 481
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "胡说，我明明听见你叫她母亲。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 483,
      "line_end": 483
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 493,
      "line_end": 493
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 499,
      "line_end": 499
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 505,
      "line_end": 505
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只因那时在下还不知道沈兄究竟是敌是友，自然只得对什么事都暂且否认的，而此刻……",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 515,
      "line_end": 515
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "沈浪，快说，他说的话完全不是真的。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 529,
      "line_end": 529
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "王兄说的话，字字句句都是真的。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 531,
      "line_end": 531
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我不信……我不信……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 533,
      "line_end": 533
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你错了……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 539,
      "line_end": 539
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你更错了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 545,
      "line_end": 545
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "误解……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 559,
      "line_end": 559
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，误解。王公子并非你所想像中的恶魔，王老夫人的所作所为，更不是你想像中的……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 561,
      "line_end": 561
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但那些事明明是我亲眼瞧见的。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 563,
      "line_end": 563
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "既是如此，她更不该将他们当作牛马一般赶来……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 587,
      "line_end": 587
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但……但……但我跟来这里，她为何又要那般对我？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 601,
      "line_end": 601
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但……但……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 609,
      "line_end": 609
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "其中秘密，自是王兄相告。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 621,
      "line_end": 621
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他告诉你的？他怎会告诉你？他怎不告诉我？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 623,
      "line_end": 623
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 625,
      "line_end": 625
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这只因到了昨夜，在下已非告诉沈兄不可。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 627,
      "line_end": 627
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "昨夜？昨夜你为何非告诉他不可？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 629,
      "line_end": 629
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不懂，不懂，我还是不懂。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 637,
      "line_end": 637
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你发现了什么破绽，我为何未发现？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 643,
      "line_end": 643
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "其实那些都是极为明显易见之事，无论谁只要稍加留意，便可发觉的，只是你那时心浮气躁……",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 645,
      "line_end": 645
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "究竟是什么，你快说吧，还穷哕嗦什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 647,
      "line_end": 647
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你可瞧见那店铺外悬的店招与对联……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 649,
      "line_end": 649
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我又不是瞎子，自然瞧见了，那是木头的招牌，刻了字以黑漆涂上，是以经久不褪，上面写着……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 651,
      "line_end": 651
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "上面写着什么，不用念了。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 653,
      "line_end": 653
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他们是老店，老店自然有老招牌，这又有什么稀奇？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 663,
      "line_end": 663
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这……这个我却未曾留意，但……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 669,
      "line_end": 669
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但这又有什么关系？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 671,
      "line_end": 671
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是呀？……为什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 677,
      "line_end": 677
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是呀！……这又为什么。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 691,
      "line_end": 691
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 697,
      "line_end": 697
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我便趁你们未曾留意时，在墙上轻轻摸了一下，我手指也立刻便被油烟染黑了，由此可见，那里不但已被烟火继续不断的熏了许久，而且最近数日前，还在被烟火熏着……",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 703,
      "line_end": 703
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这句话我有些不懂，你再说清楚些好么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 705,
      "line_end": 705
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "要知墙壁若要被烟火熏黑，必定要一段极长的时间。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 707,
      "line_end": 707
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但我用手一摸，染在我手上的油烟，却是新迹，这自然可见那些地方在最近几年中，一直都在被烟火熏着……",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 713,
      "line_end": 713
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哦，我明白了……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 715,
      "line_end": 715
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但我还是不明白，这又有什么关系？",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 717,
      "line_end": 717
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有两点重要的关系。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 719,
      "line_end": 719
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "死人，你快说呀！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 721,
      "line_end": 721
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，真奇怪……还有第二点呢。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 727,
      "line_end": 727
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是呀，这又是为什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 733,
      "line_end": 733
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "走出店门，你便可断定了？你凭什么断定的？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 739,
      "line_end": 739
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我发现那棺材店隔壁，乃是家香烛铺。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 741,
      "line_end": 741
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "搬家……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 751,
      "line_end": 751
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "正是搬家，那棺材铺的后院，昔日本是香烛铺制造香烛的所在，墙壁自然早就被烟火熏黑了……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 753,
      "line_end": 753
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错……不错……不错……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 759,
      "line_end": 759
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 761,
      "line_end": 761
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我知道了……我明白了……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 763,
      "line_end": 763
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你且说说你知道了什么？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 765,
      "line_end": 765
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好，你总算明白了。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 771,
      "line_end": 771
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "也并不太简单，还是要费些工夫的。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 777,
      "line_end": 777
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他那两只鬼眼睛，本就比别人厉害。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 799,
      "line_end": 799
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "沈兄当时完全不动声色，在下也丝毫未曾发觉沈兄已窥破了这其中的秘密，但到了那日晚间……",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 813,
      "line_end": 813
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你吹牛也未遇着敌手。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 823,
      "line_end": 823
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小酒鬼遇着大酒鬼，自然要吃苦了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 829,
      "line_end": 829
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "沈浪，你老实说，你那时到哪里去了？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 835,
      "line_end": 835
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你……你杀了他？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 851,
      "line_end": 851
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这些鬼花样我也知道得不少。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 873,
      "line_end": 873
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你知道个屁。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 875,
      "line_end": 875
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "要佳人骂我一句，当真是颇不容易。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 877,
      "line_end": 877
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她对你怎样？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 887,
      "line_end": 887
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "打起来了没有？谁打胜了？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 893,
      "line_end": 893
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她对你说了些什么？",
      "tone": "冷哼",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 907,
      "line_end": 907
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我听她老人家说出一切后，自然除了请她老人家恕我冒昧闯入之罪外，还要请她老人家继续主持此事，我虽无用，也少不得要为此事稍尽绵薄之力……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 915,
      "line_end": 915
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但在她老人家话还未说完之前，却还有段趣事。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 921,
      "line_end": 921
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么趣事？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 923,
      "line_end": 923
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那便是你两人……",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 925,
      "line_end": 925
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我两人又怎样？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 927,
      "line_end": 927
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不要说了……不要说了……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 933,
      "line_end": 933
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只因那时事态还未分明，我一来生怕你闯入后胡乱发作，怒恼了王老夫人，也坏了大事，二来……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 939,
      "line_end": 939
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不瞒王兄，正是如此。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 947,
      "line_end": 947
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "由此可见，沈兄全属好意……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 949,
      "line_end": 949
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我……我……",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 959,
      "line_end": 959
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "今日午后，我与沈兄已将此事始末告诉了这猫儿……",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 961,
      "line_end": 961
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是么？他们可是早已告诉了你？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 963,
      "line_end": 963
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好像是的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 965,
      "line_end": 965
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那酒不错……咳……咳……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 971,
      "line_end": 971
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我的头有些晕晕的，但……但还未那么醉。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 977,
      "line_end": 977
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "解释什么？有什么好解释的？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 989,
      "line_end": 989
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但此事委实怪不得熊兄。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 991,
      "line_end": 991
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不怪他怪谁？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 993,
      "line_end": 993
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你可曾注意，今日有个人你始终未曾瞧见。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 995,
      "line_end": 995
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他想必也已发现了什么，所以乘夜走了……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 1005,
      "line_end": 1005
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你不肯将秘密告诉我，为何又告诉了那死猫？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 1013,
      "line_end": 1013
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只是熊兄决不敢泄露其中秘密，而你……",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 1015,
      "line_end": 1015
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我怎样？难道我是长舌妇，多嘴婆？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 1017,
      "line_end": 1017
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，我天生直肠直肚，我本就是直心眼儿，不像你们这样沉得住气，不像你们这么诡计多端，但……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 1023,
      "line_end": 1023
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这个……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 1029,
      "line_end": 1029
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "其实这也……",
      "tone": "陈述",
