      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "朱姑娘，留步。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 1071,
      "line_end": 1071
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你……你真的让她走么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 1075,
      "line_end": 1075
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这个熊兄只管放心，她走不远的。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 1087,
      "line_end": 1087
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "走不远？为什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 1089,
      "line_end": 1089
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不会错……但愿不会错。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 1101,
